7c9dfb6f5b812155","tid":1220304,"uid":4619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b15807f3a4be64ece9f16608f1d3d6fb79b500","tid":1220304,"uid":93451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:20:25.000Z","msg":"岩岩因為宗教 po 我發現到<br />\n一但上左熱門 就好容易比人操作到輿論<br />\n上左熱門好容易比人利用<br />\n因為好多人見到個po就咁like左就算 令一d 未有驗證 同未有討論既事 比人帶左風向<br />\n<br />\n所以開返下邊個po提下大家 希望大家幫手推到上到熱門<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1220056/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1220056/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有時講錯左野就好容易比人利用<br />\n見到唔同既消息大家記得同周邊既朋友傾多啲<br />\n驗清楚真假 同諗清楚個樣野既後果<br />\n係而家信息過多既時間<br />\n思考係十分重要既一步<br />\n大家坐埋一條船 尊重係好重要既一樣野<br />\npushhh</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n上邊紅字係我覺得依幾日 時時刻mon po 既結論<br />\n希望大家幫下手like <br />\n睇到聖經po發現有啲人 真係會like左就算唔會諗<br />\nlike 係好容易比人帶左風向<br />\n想上到熱門提到大家<br />\n<br />\n南亞仔可唔可以都幫手推下<br />\n有時9 like真係好容易比人帶左風向利用"},{"pid":"77ec5c8442521770e1f476dfe914a32c4268153b","tid":1220304,"uid":131326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"香港警察 社會垃圾<br />\n人民奴隸 賣港惡賊<br />\n底層散仔毅進弱智仔<br />\n就算大學學歷都係垃圾科，無得揀先去做警犬嘅廢柴，蛇鼠一窩"},{"pid":"46c85c0b2eb8db670e44bde02f30f59db823befa","tid":1220304,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22b15807f3a4be64ece9f16608f1d3d6fb79b500","tid":1220304,"uid":93451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:20:25.000Z","msg":"岩岩因為宗教 po 我發現到<br />\n一但上左熱門 就好容易比人操作到輿論<br />\n上左熱門好容易比人利用<br />\n因為好多人見到個po就咁like左就算 令一d 未有驗證 同未有討論既事 比人帶左風向<br />\n<br />\n所以開返下邊個po提下大家 希望大家幫手推到上到熱門<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1220056/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1220056/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有時講錯左野就好容易比人利用<br />\n見到唔同既消息大家記得同周邊既朋友傾多啲<br />\n驗清楚真假 同諗清楚個樣野既後果<br />\n係而家信息過多既時間<br />\n思考係十分重要既一步<br />\n大家坐埋一條船 尊重係好重要既一樣野<br />\npushhh</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n上邊紅字係我覺得依幾日 時時刻mon po 既結論<br />\n希望大家幫下手like <br />\n睇到聖經po發現有啲人 真係會like左就算唔會諗<br />\nlike 係好容易比人帶左風向<br />\n想上到熱門提到大家<br />\n<br />\n南亞仔可唔可以都幫手推下<br />\n有時9 like真係好容易比人帶左風向利用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:22:44.000Z","msg":"收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d925536ddff605f41ec3c323a8c0f8adc466983","tid":1220304,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79aec4a1d463eee3e51354f095c5299d7b8110c6","tid":1220304,"uid":258513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"117ce152a56fe88734cb32b88d443fe51ae67819","tid":1220304,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daab9968307d5750a95f38e3ff3295436df8c285","tid":1220304,"uid":258513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:10:23.000Z","msg":"樓主喺自己youtube channel 都講埋啦不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:11:25.000Z","msg":"個youtuber 唔係我嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:12:03.000Z","msg":"sor 搞錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:23:14.000Z","msg":"唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b165b13c113b17d70bb77dcdc75596b5f778a8b7","tid":1220304,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77ec5c8442521770e1f476df